# ─── Credential-bearing file classes (2026-07-16) ────────────
# These leaked real keys once. Deploy runbooks paste admin tokens and
# deployment IDs inline; one-shot Setup*Key* scripts hardcode a vendor key
# by design and are meant to be deleted after running. Neither belongs here.
DEPLOY_*.md
RECOVERY_*.md
gmail-apps-script/Setup*Key*.gs
secretmap.json
